  23 Jan 2004; <gustavoz@gentoo.org> glademm-2.0.0.ebuild:
  stable on sparc

*glademm-2.0.0.1 (20 Nov 2003)

  20 Nov 2003; Alastair Tse <liquidx@gentoo.org> glademm-2.0.0.1.ebuild:
  version bump

  12 Nov 2003; Luca Barbato <lu_zero@gentoo.org> glademm-2.0.0.ebuild:
  Marked ~ppc

  02 Oct 2003; Joshua Kinard <kumba@gentoo.org> glademm-2.0.0.ebuild:
  Added a patch that fixes a missing <cassert> include that allows glademm to
  compile with gcc-3.3.x.
  Closes Bug #29654

  13 Jul 2003; Martin Holzer <mholzer@gentoo.org> glademm-0.6.4.ebuild:
  update x11-libs/gtkmm to dev-cpp/gtkmm

  21 Jun 2003; Alastair Tse <liquidx@gentoo.org> glademm-0.6.4.ebuild:
  fix deps for dev-cpp move for gnomemm

*glademm-2.0.0 (09 May 2003)

  09 May 2003; foser <foser@gentoo.org> glademm-2.0.0.ebuild :
  First stable release, fixed deps (aka removed 'em)

